<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Hosela Ornament — Angsa Kristal Premium Dashboard</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #c9a458;
    --gold-light: #e8cc8a;
    --gold-pale: #f5e6c0;
    --dark: #0d0a06;
    --dark2: #1a1208;
    --dark3: #241a0e;
    --cream: #fdf6ec;
    --cream2: #f5ead6;
    --text: #2a1f0e;
    --text-soft: #6b5540;
    --rose: #c8847a;
    --rose-light: #e8b4ae;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--cream);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NOISE TEXTURE OVERLAY ─── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, #2a1a08 0%, #0d0a06 60%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 24px 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px; right: -100px;
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,164,88,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px; left: -80px;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,132,122,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .brand-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }
  .brand-tag::before, .brand-tag::after {
    content: '';
    width: 30px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .hero-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 320px;
    height: 320px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 0.4s;
  }
  .hero-img-wrap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,164,88,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .hero-img-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 200px; height: 30px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(201,164,88,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.2);
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 9vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.6s;
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.75s;
  }

  .price-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.9s;
  }
  .price-old {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.3);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .price-badge {
    background: var(--rose);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .price-new {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 1s;
  }
  .price-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.4);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 1.05s;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a458 0%, #e8cc8a 50%, #c9a458 100%);
    color: var(--dark);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 18px 48px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 360px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 1.2s;
  }
  .cta-btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: -100%;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
    transition: left 0.5s ease;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover::before { left: 100%; }
  .cta-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(201,164,88,0.35); }

  .cta-sub {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.4);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 1.35s;
  }
  .cta-sub span { color: var(--rose-light); }

  /* ─── TRUST BAR ─── */
  .trust-bar {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.1);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 0 28px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.15);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .trust-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .trust-icon { font-size: 20px; }
  .trust-text { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(245,230,192,0.6); letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .trust-text strong { display: block; color: var(--gold-light); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }

  /* ─── SECTION BASE ─── */
  section { padding: 80px 24px; }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-tag::before {
    content: '';
    width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 7vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-light); }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.6);
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  /* ─── PROBLEM/DESIRE ─── */
  .desire {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark) 0%, var(--dark2) 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .desire-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .desire .section-tag { justify-content: center; }
  .desire .section-tag::before { display: none; }
  .desire .section-desc { margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; }

  .quote-block {
    margin: 40px 0;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201,164,88,0.05);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .quote-block p {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--cream2);
  }
  .quote-block span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.35);
  }

  /* ─── FEATURES ─── */
  .features {
    background: var(--dark3);
  }
  .features-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .feat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .feat-card {
    background: rgba(201,164,88,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .feat-card:hover {
    background: rgba(201,164,88,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(201,164,88,0.25);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .feat-card.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .feat-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }
  .feat-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .feat-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.5);
  }

  /* ─── PRODUCT SHOWCASE ─── */
  .showcase {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, #1e1206 0%, var(--dark) 70%);
  }
  .showcase-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .showcase-img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 0 1px rgba(201,164,88,0.05);
  }

  .spec-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .spec-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.08);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.65);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .spec-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .spec-check {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-top: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ─── TESTIMONIALS ─── */
  .testis {
    background: var(--dark2);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .testis-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .testis .section-tag { justify-content: center; }
  .testis .section-tag::before { display: none; }

  .testi-grid {
    margin-top: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .testi-card {
    background: rgba(201,164,88,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .testi-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .testi-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--cream2);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .testi-author { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(245,230,192,0.4); letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .testi-author strong { color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ─── URGENCY ─── */
  .urgency {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a0a 0%, #0d0605 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,132,122,0.2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,132,122,0.2);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }
  .urgency-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .stock-bar {
    background: rgba(200,132,122,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,132,122,0.25);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .stock-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose-light);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .stock-track {
    height: 4px;
    background: rgba(200,132,122,0.15);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .stock-fill {
    height: 100%;
    width: 78%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--rose), var(--rose-light));
    border-radius: 2px;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.7; } }
  .stock-count { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(245,230,192,0.4); }
  .stock-count strong { color: var(--rose-light); }

  .urgency-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 7vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .urgency-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rose-light); }

  .urgency-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .warning-list {
    list-style: none;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .warning-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.6);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .warn-icon { color: var(--rose-light); flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 1px; }

  /* ─── FINAL CTA ─── */
  .final-cta {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, #2a1a08 0%, var(--dark) 70%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 24px 100px;
  }
  .final-inner { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .divider::before, .divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold));
    opacity: 0.3;
  }
  .divider::after { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent); }
  .divider-icon { color: var(--gold); font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.6; }

  .final-price-old {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.25);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .final-price-new {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .final-price-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .cta-btn-large {
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a458 0%, #e8cc8a 50%, #c9a458 100%);
    color: var(--dark);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 22px 48px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-btn-large::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: -100%;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
    transition: left 0.5s ease;
  }
  .cta-btn-large:hover::before { left: 100%; }
  .cta-btn-large:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(201,164,88,0.4); }

  .guarantee-note {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.3);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .guarantee-note strong { color: rgba(245,230,192,0.5); font-weight: 400; }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: #080604;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,164,88,0.08);
  }
  footer p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(245,230,192,0.2);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ─── SCROLL REVEAL ─── */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="brand-tag">Hosela Ornament Collection</div>
    
    <div class="hero-img-wrap">
      <img class="hero-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Angsa Kristal Premium Hosela">
    </div>

    <h1 class="hero-title">Sentuhan <em>Mewah</em><br>di Setiap Perjalanan</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Angsa Kristal Premium — Dashboard Ornament</p>

    <div class="price-block">
      <span class="price-old">Rp499.000</span>
      <span class="price-badge">Hemat 52%</span>
    </div>
    <div class="price-new">Rp239.000</div>
    <p class="price-note">Harga spesial · Terbatas untuk hari ini</p>

    <a href="#order" class="cta-btn">✦ Dapatkan Sekarang</a>
    <p class="cta-sub">Gratis Ongkir · COD Tersedia · <span>Stok Sangat Terbatas</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ TRUST BAR ═══ -->
<div class="trust-bar">
  <div class="trust-item">
    <span class="trust-icon">⭐</span>
    <div class="trust-text"><strong>4.9 / 5.0</strong>Rating Pembeli</div>
  </div>
  <div class="trust-item">
    <span class="trust-icon">📦</span>
    <div class="trust-text"><strong>1.200+</strong>Terjual</div>
  </div>
  <div class="trust-item">
    <span class="trust-icon">🚚</span>
    <div class="trust-text"><strong>COD</strong>Bayar di Tempat</div>
  </div>
  <div class="trust-item">
    <span class="trust-icon">🔄</span>
    <div class="trust-text"><strong>Garansi</strong>Produk Original</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ DESIRE ═══ -->
<section class="desire">
  <div class="desire-inner reveal">
    <div class="section-tag">Untuk Kamu Yang Menghargai Detail</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Mobil Bukan Sekadar<br>Kendaraan, <em>Ia Cerminan Dirimu</em></h2>
    
    <div class="quote-block">
      <p>"Perempuan yang elegan tahu bahwa keindahan ada di detail terkecil — termasuk ruang pribadinya di balik kemudi."</p>
      <span>— Hosela Ornament Philosophy</span>
    </div>

    <p class="section-desc">
      Kamu menghabiskan jam-jam terbaik harimu di dalam mobil. Mengantar anak, pergi kerja, momen sendiri yang berharga. Bukankah ruang itu layak mendapatkan sentuhan yang seindah dirimu?
    </p>
  </div>
